   "source": [
    "# 07 - Full Pipeline Evaluation & Ablation Study\n",
    "\n",
    "**Goal**: Evaluate complete system end-to-end\n",
    "\n",
    "**Components**:\n",
    "1. Text classification (DeBERTa)\n",
    "2. Evidence retrieval (Tavily)\n",
    "3. Cross-encoder reranking\n",
    "4. Image verification (Gemini Vision)\n",
    "5. Spread detection\n",
    "6. Explainability\n",
    "\n",
    "**Ablation**: Test impact of removing each component"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, precision_recall_fscore_support\n",
    "import time\n",
    "\n",
    "sns.set_style('whitegrid')\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Load Test Dataset"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Load holdout test set\n",
    "test_df = pd.read_csv('../eval_holdout.csv')\n",
    "print(f\"Test set: {len(test_df)} samples\")\n",
    "print(test_df['label'].value_counts())"
   ]
  }
 ],
